This sytem of norms is inspired by Childress and Beauchamp's Principlism:

Values: 
Value 1 - Non-maleficence (do no harm)
Value 2 - Benevolence (promote happiness)

Duties: 
Duty 1 - Respect other people autonomous choices
Duty 2 - Help other people take their autonomous choices (e.g., by providing them enough information)

Ranking:
Duty 1 > Value 1 > Duty 2 > Value 2
